n against Carini on Thursday,the International Olympic Committee (IOC) hit out at the treatment the Algerian has received.\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.8896086252880064, \"rank\": 0.12408982059535306, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9741790254106494, \"rank\": 0.026456746161254072, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's win\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"the treatment\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The current aggression against these two athletes is based entirely on this arbitrary decision, which was taken without any proper procedure especially considering that these athletes had been competing in top-level competition for many years,' the statement from the IOC read.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0369549838032524e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The current aggression\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"these two athletes\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"this arbitrary decision\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"any proper procedure\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"top-level competition\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0369549838032524e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"the two athletes\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every person has the right to practise sport without discrimination.'\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every person\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week, the IBA criticised the IOC's decision to allow Lin and Khelif to compete in Paris.\", \"from\